{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I would walk at the end, always at the end, with four or five children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Never more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And hold back, hold back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And just as the children turned the last corner, move them into where one of the guys stood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then these children would be sent all over the country to farmers or-- or whoever was safe and would take them in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now everybody in the Schouwberg had name tags, which never made any sense.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What for?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the only time that it made sense, because that's where the children had name tags.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could take off the name tags and one of the other guys in the theater, in the Schouwburg, could look for the parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we walked around 4 o'clock, and the transport never left until 11:00, 11:30 at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So plenty of time to find the parents of these children and tell them your children will be safe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will be sent to such and such a place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this worked wonderful for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know, perhaps six weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got so many children that we could go two, three times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you see, there again the-- the crazy thing, nobody ever counted the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody ever wondered that there were much more for lunch than there were for-- for dinner when we came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody counted them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was very easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Easy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not so easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because first of all, when it came to who do you choose, how you can make-- how can you make that decision which child should be safe and which child should not be safe?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a terrible thing to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When it came to it, I disappeared in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't want to make this decision.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
